        mid-tier lands in mid-market kitchens across the Valley, San Gabriel Valley, and Westside mid-
        market. Frigidaire Professional premium lands in mid-premium kitchen remodels alongside KitchenAid
        counter-depth installs, typically in Westside and Valley premium-kitchen households.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
